      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t中共没有取消，只是因为被病毒击穿了清零防疫政策而已，然后被迫放开。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGUxNjhmYTUzY2YyNGY1MTc1YzhkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0e168fa53cf24f5175c8d.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0e168fa53cf24f5175c8d.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0e168fa53cf24f5175c8d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
